channel.title: Feedback :: My Hugo Site
channel.description: Overall Evaluation 1. Working Environment The working environment is friendly and welcoming. Everyone is willing to support and motivate each other in their tasks. The workspace is modern, tidy, and comfortable. 2. Support from Mentor / Team Admin The mentors and admin team members always provide clear and detailed guidance, as well as support with procedures and learning materials, helping me complete the internship process smoothly. They are also willing to share knowledge based on their personal work experience. 3. Relevance of Work to Academic Major
